## ðŸ§© Code Snippet:

### ðŸ”¹ 1832. Check if the Sentence Is Pangram
```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    bool checkIfPangram(string sentence) {
        map<int, int> mp;
        for (char c : sentence) {
            mp[c]++;
        }
        return mp.size() == 26;
    }
};
